1. Create a new Dynamic Web Application in Eclipse
2. create "lib" directory under the "WebContent\WEB-INF" directory

javax.servlet.jsp.jstl-1.2.1
javax.servlet.jsp.jstl-api-1.2.1

3. Create "view" directory under the "WebContent\WEB-INF" directory


a. Create Controller class
b. Define Controller method
c. Add Request Mapping to Controller method
d. Return View Name
e. Develop View Page